data.name: GetAccessories
data.value: Select AccessoriesId, AccessoryTypeId, Accessory, Price from [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[Accessories] where DeletedDate is null

data.name: GetAccessorybyId
data.value: Select AccessoryTypeId, Accessory, Price from [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[Accessories] where DeletedDate is null and AccessoriesId = @accessoriesId

data.name: InsertAccessory
data.value: Insert into [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[Accessories] (AccessoryTypeId, Accessory, Price, CreatedDate) values (@accessoryTypeId, @accessory, @price, @createdDate)

data.name: UpdateAccessory
data.value: Update [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[Accessories] set Accessory = @accessory, Price = @price, ModifiedDate = @modifiedDate where AccessoriesId = @accessoriesId

data.name: GetVehicleName
data.value: Select VehicleNameId, CompanyId, VehicleName, from [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[VehicleName] where DeletedDate is null

data.name: GetVehicleNamebyId
data.value: Select CompanyId, VehicleName from [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[VehicleName] where DeletedDate is null and VehicleNameId = @vehicleNameId

data.name: UpdateAccessory
data.value: Update [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[VehicleName] set VehicleName = @vehicleName, ModifiedDate = @modifiedDate where VehicleNameId = @vehicleNameId
